                </div>

                <div class="square-card bg-transparent flex flex-col justify-between gap-7 items-center">
                    <Image src={Design} alt="Design" />
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Design</div>
                        <p class="text-lg text-pretty text-neutral-300">Where we concept initial page layouts in Figma/Sketch. We're receptive to feedback all throughout. Once the designs are 80% complete, we push them to development, where pixel perfection is achieved.</p>
